\r\n　　此　致\r\n臺灣宜蘭地方法院\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　 111　　年　　6 　　月　　13　　日\r\n                              檢　察　官  林小刊","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ILDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c415%2c20220830%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ILDM,111,交簡,415,20220830,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"415","JDATE":"20220830","JTITLE":"公共危險"}